column2: NPS APPRAISAL PIGEON RIVER NPS LAKES
sunny-light wind- Gene Meyer with me. Took water sample.
calm day. 2 boy's fishing from dock. Afew duck's also on lake.
sunny-light wind. kid's sming from their own dock west side of lake.

Light chop on the lake. A man and his 2 kid's(boy and girl) just came off from fishing. Caught a bunch of small panfish. Not much going on at the lake. I went around the lake and only seen small panfish. Nothing feeding on the surface. Real nice day to be on the water..
pollen on water surface. Sunny day.
